column5: I'm sure that most of you have seen this picture before, but I think that it deserves to be shown again. Look at the size of the head on this thing? It's about 3 times bigger than any of the childrens heads. Unbelieveable!!!
Sure some happy faces there Dan. Never seen it before.  Thanks   BTW What are you doing on your sundays now  Atleast I got the bow hunt still.
WOW....thats a huge monster pike for sure depending on what he used he might even have a world line class record as well and not even know about it......
That's a fish and a half!
Beauty native-caught northern!  Seen it before, but do you notice the marks behind the gill? Looks like a 3 or 4 prong fish spear got it.
I can't believe that was 99. I it seems like it was only a year to 2 ago
caught in 99, still eating it today!
Sure is a huge pike, but 70 inches or 80lbs it's not  LOL. I would guesstimate it at maybe 56 inches and 40 lbs max. Still an unbelievable pike.
Now I eat alot of fish but not sure how that one would taste  , sure would be fun to catch though  Doug
